  "2360440": {
    "name": "Dreamians: Card Battle",
    "steam_appid": 2360440,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360440/extras/acc9d91b58e0f8403ca987ddf5b1522a.poster.avif?t=1750129282\" width=600 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360440/extras/acc9d91b58e0f8403ca987ddf5b1522a.webm?t=1750129282\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360440/extras/acc9d91b58e0f8403ca987ddf5b1522a.mp4?t=1750129282\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dreamians: Card Battle是一款Roguelike Deckbuilder游戏，其中的生物在战斗中可以进化，并以意想不到的方式改变战斗的走向。游戏有三个主要的Dreamians，分别是半红龙半狗的Dragnis，蓝狼Wolfae和噩梦蝙蝠Kalek。每个Dreamians都有自己的能力和解决方案来应对游戏中的挑战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在Dreamians: Card Battle中，玩家将进入Dreamians的世界，这个世界只能在我们睡觉时或者被放置在一台特殊机器中连接到这个世界时才能访问，这会导致睡眠并强制进行强大的灵魂投射。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dreamians的世界正在被可怕的Oníricos旅行者入侵，他们想要夺取尽可能多的梦。玩家和他的Dreamian需要在通过森林、山脉、破碎的城市、火焰之路甚至扭曲的维度的5个地图上赢得激烈的战斗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360440/extras/425b052db703a52459244c925611a229.poster.avif?t=1750129282\" width=600 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360440/extras/425b052db703a52459244c925611a229.webm?t=1750129282\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360440/extras/425b052db703a52459244c925611a229.mp4?t=1750129282\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>数字 -</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >+100 - 用于游戏的卡片。这些是攻击、防御和特殊卡片。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >+40 - 修改Dreamian属性的梦之宝石。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >+30 - 不同形式的敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5 - Oníricos旅行者。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4 - 不同的场景。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>了解Dreamians：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360440/extras/54ddf49e49ceb358486bc86d29b34944.avif?t=1750129282\" width=600 height=206 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dragnis: </strong>一只半龙半狗的生物。他非常温顺忠诚，但当需要时也会攻击。他喜欢儿童笑话，非常倔强。 Dragnis可以进化为更强大的Draghium和Dragnor形态。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360440/extras/fc2edf567b2c0e8574f01724b1de9864.avif?t=1750129282\" width=600 height=206 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Wolfae: </strong>不要被他可爱的外表所欺骗。他是一位出色的战士。他等待着合适的时机发动攻击，并且可以进化为两种非常强大的形态：Wofaion和Vuk。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360440/extras/7fd1a23d167ca9e0ffacb7a8052b812c.avif?t=1750129282\" width=600 height=206 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Kalek:</strong> 他是从一个被击败的噩梦中诞生的。现在他与梦见他的人类相处得很好。他的长翅膀让他能够高飞，他的大耳朵让他听得很清楚。当他的纹身发光时，他知道攻击来了。他可以进化为两种形态：Kalan和Kaliel。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360440/extras/da250988fbaca18b5da8437551435c9d.poster.avif?t=1750129282\" width=600 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360440/extras/da250988fbaca18b5da8437551435c9d.webm?t=1750129282\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360440/extras/da250988fbaca18b5da8437551435c9d.mp4?t=1750129282\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Delirium的时间！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当玩家填满特殊的进化条时，Delirium就会被激活。如果玩家拥有特殊的Delirium卡片，他可以将他的可爱生物进化为更致命的形态。每个Dreamian都有两种Delirium形态：HyperDelirium版本和MegaDelirium版本。这是一个有趣且非常有用的动态，可以帮助您赢得更困难的战斗。</p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语, 法语, 意大利语, 德语, 简体中文, 西班牙语 - 拉丁美洲, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西, 俄语, 韩语, 日语",
